<h3>Frequently Asked Questions</h3>
<ul>
  <li><strong>How do I sign up?</strong> – Visit the <%= link_to "Sign Up", signup_path %> page and fill in your information.</li>
  <li><strong>How do I log in?</strong> – Go to the <%= link_to "Log In", login_path %> page and enter your credentials.</li>
